OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777097136
OL,3,C'I want him to be proud of me' ` MP
OL,4,Crunning London Marathon in brother's
OL,5,Cmemory
OL,7,FA Labour MP will run the London
OL,8,FMarathon in tribute to his older
OL,9,Fbrother, who died last year from a
OL,10,Frare cancer.
OL,12,FJosh Fenton-Glynn will run the 26.2
OL,13,Fmiles through the capital in memory of
OL,14,Fhis brother, Alex English, who died in
OL,15,FJanuary 2025 just two weeks short of
OL,16,Fhis 53rd birthday.
OL,18,FThe Calder Valley MP is among a host
OL,19,Fof parliamentarians from across the
OL,20,Fpolitical spectrum who are taking on
OL,21,Fthe challenge this year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777097136
OL,3,C'I want him to be proud of me' ` MP
OL,4,Crunning London Marathon in brother's
OL,5,Cmemory
OL,7,FThis will be his seventh marathon, and
OL,8,Fhis second London Marathon after
OL,9,Fcompleting the race last year.
OL,11,FBut this year's personal cause is
OL,12,Fparticularly striking, Mr Fenton-Glynn
OL,13,Fsaid.
OL,15,F"I do a lot of things I do in life
OL,16,Fbecause I believe in people, I care
OL,17,Fabout people, but there's something
OL,18,Fquite different doing something for
OL,19,Fyour brother," he told the Press
OL,20,FAssociation.
OL,26,@wD@AOU{D@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777097136
OL,3,C'I want him to be proud of me' ` MP
OL,4,Crunning London Marathon in brother's
OL,5,Cmemory
OL,7,F"One of my motivations in life has
OL,8,Falways been wanting him to be proud of
OL,9,Fme."
OL,11,FThe MP's brother died from high-grade
OL,12,Facinic cell carcinoma, a rare form of
OL,13,Fsalivary gland cancer.
OL,15,FMr Fenton-Glynn is raising money for
OL,16,Ftwo charities this year: Salivary
OL,17,FGland Cancer UK, and Cancer 52.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@DO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777097136
OL,3,C'I want him to be proud of me' ` MP
OL,4,Crunning London Marathon in brother's
OL,5,Cmemory
OL,7,FThe second of these is aimed at
OL,8,Fworking to improve outcomes for the
OL,9,F55% of cancer deaths caused by rare
OL,10,Fforms of the disease.
OL,12,F"Life felt very unfair (when he died).
OL,13,FHe was one of the best people I ever
OL,14,Fmet. He died in a way that I wouldn't
OL,15,Fwish on the worst people," Mr Fenton-
OL,16,FGlynn said.
OL,26,@tD@AOUwD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
