OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777097136
OL,3,C'I want him to be proud of me' ` MP
OL,4,Crunning London Marathon in brother's
OL,5,Cmemory
OL,7,F"It's that moment in the last few
OL,8,Fweeks, he had lost his sight and most
OL,9,Fof his ability to speak, and could
OL,10,Fstill make a brief joke about Monty
OL,11,FPython in the middle and I remember
OL,12,Fwhen I was talking to a doctor, he was
OL,13,Ftold he wasn't strong enough to be
OL,14,Fpart of any clinical trials, his first
OL,15,Fresponse was telling the doctor he
OL,16,Fdidn't agree.
OL,18,F"I wish there were more opportunities
OL,19,Ffor him at the time and there were
OL,20,Fmore trials open."
OL,26,@oD@AOUzD@AOU|D@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777097136
OL,3,C'I want him to be proud of me' ` MP
OL,4,Crunning London Marathon in brother's
OL,5,Cmemory
OL,7,FHe added: "The Christmas before, he
OL,8,Fhad called me to tell me he had a bit
OL,9,Fof a lump on his face and it might be
OL,10,Fcancer, but it probably wasn't, and if
OL,11,Fit is cancer, it's a very treatable
OL,12,Fform.
OL,14,F"But it was a fast-acting version.
OL,16,F"They have only ever identified about
OL,17,F100 cases of that, but with more
OL,18,Finvestment into rare cancers, we would
OL,19,Fprobably have identified more.
OL,26,@oD@KOUvD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777097136
OL,3,C'I want him to be proud of me' ` MP
OL,4,Crunning London Marathon in brother's
OL,5,Cmemory
OL,7,F"There were various points where it
OL,8,Ffelt pretty tough.
OL,10,F"He had a 14-hour operation to have
OL,11,Fthe tumour removed, but then it grew
OL,12,Fback.
OL,14,F"By summer that year (2024) they said
OL,15,Fhe probably had 18 months to live, but
OL,16,Fhe had about six months."
OL,18,FMr English was at one point in the
OL,19,F1990s "big in Japan" with his indie
OL,20,Fband Eva Luna.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@AOUvD@AOUxD@YO]{D@GOU{D@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/20
