CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777097136
OL,3,C'I want him to be proud of me' ` MP
OL,4,Crunning London Marathon in brother's
OL,5,Cmemory
OL,7,F"Also, I couldn't say no to the chief
OL,8,Fwhip," Ms Morgan, who is running for
OL,9,Fthe charities Lingen Davies and Hope
OL,10,FHouse, added.
OL,12,FFor Lib Dem chief whip Ms Chamberlain,
OL,13,Fit will be her first marathon.
OL,15,FThe North East Fife MP, a former
OL,16,Fshinty player, got into running at the
OL,17,Fstart of 2025, and is raising money
OL,18,Ffor two charities: the Fife Carers'
OL,19,FCentre, and PANS PANDAS, which
OL,20,Fsupports children with rare
OL,21,Fneuropsychiatric conditions.
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@FO]
