FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30418
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777097136
OL,3,C'I want him to be proud of me' ` MP
OL,4,Crunning London Marathon in brother's
OL,5,Cmemory
OL,7,F"Other than that I have been listening
OL,8,Fto a bit of Sophie Ellis-Bextor's
OL,9,FSongs From The Kitchen Disco," he
OL,10,Fadded.
OL,12,FMr Wild, who is running for men's
OL,13,Fmental health charity the 8:56
OL,14,FFoundation, has previously been able
OL,15,Fto boast of being the "fastest English
OL,16,FMP", beaten only by now-ex MP for the
OL,17,FVale of Glamorgan Alun Cairns when
OL,18,Fthey both ran in 2024.
OL,20,FThe 2026 race will be his sixth
OL,21,Fmarathon, and his fourth as an MP.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@^O]wD@WOUxD@CO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/20
