SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777097136
OL,3,C'I want him to be proud of me' ` MP
OL,4,Crunning London Marathon in brother's
OL,5,Cmemory
OL,7,FFor Conservative former minister
OL,8,FRichard Holden by contrast, it will be
OL,9,Fhis first.
OL,11,F"I've basically gone from couch to
OL,12,Fmarathon in five months," he told PA.
OL,14,FThe Basildon and Billericay MP,
OL,15,Frunning for St Luke's Hospice, began
OL,16,Fto take an interest in running last
OL,17,Fyear, after vowing to become more
OL,18,Factive when he gave up smoking in
OL,19,FOctober 2024.
