OL,3,C'I want him to be proud of me' ` MP
OL,4,Crunning London Marathon in brother's
OL,5,Cmemory
OL,7,FOn Sunday, Mr Holden is likely to be
OL,8,Feasy for spectators to spot in his
OL,9,Fstandout legwear.
OL,11,F"I've got a pair of very snazzy Union
OL,12,FJack running shorts. I got them from a
OL,13,Fcompany in Southend on the
OL,14,Frecommendation of a friend of mine who
OL,15,Fhas done a marathon previously," he
OL,16,Ftold PA.
OL,18,F"They, along with Body Glide, have
OL,19,Fbeen saviours of mine, because I
OL,20,Fstarted to get severe chafing."
